


The internal structure of herbstluftwm is as follows:

all boxes are C-Modules (e.g. $name.c-files)


                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                    
                           X11                                                                                                      
                            |                                                                                                       
                            V                                                                                                       
                        +--------+  key  +-----+ call  +---------+                                                                  
                        |  main  |------>| key |------>| command |                                                                  
                        +--------+ event +-----+       +---------+                                                                  
                            \                    output /  ^                                                                        
                     IPC-Call\      +------------+<----'  / Execute                                                                 
                      -Window `---->| ipc-server |-------'  IPC-Call                                                                
                        -Event      +------------+                                                                                  
                                           |                                                                                        
                                           V                                                                                        
                                          X11                                                                                       
herbstclient is rather simple:

 Command-Line-   +------+
   Arguments --->| main |----.
                 |      |   X11
    stdout  <----|      |<---'
                 +------+






